mixin text-samples
  ul.text-samples
    li.text-samples__item.text-samples__item--h1
      h3.text-samples__title H1
      p.text-samples__text This one is the sub-section or widget title

    li.text-samples__item.text-samples__item--h2
      h3.text-samples__title H2
      p.text-samples__text Next one is the item title inside widgets

    li.text-samples__item.text-samples__item--h3
      h3.text-samples__title H3
      p.text-samples__text This is a label or CTA text

    li.text-samples__item.text-samples__item--body
      h3.text-samples__title Body
      p.text-samples__text This is the body text which is used for most of the design, like paragraphs, lists, etc.